{"tid":166413,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"如果辭了職，佢可不可以炒我？","createTime":"2017-03-22T05:55:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-25T03:35:24.000Z","uid":68430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1b6fb744c7e48805a51a860716dd6805360bf391","tid":166413,"uid":68430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T05:55:28.000Z","msg":"按一般既僱傭合約。<br />\n<br />\n如果我辭了職，在通知期內，lets say 表現不達標，公司可否炒我？<br />\n<br />\n如果在未離職時，表現不達標，公司想炒，又要不要賠錢的？<br />\n<br />\n(sorry 我沒有提供僱傭合約，但如果按一般情況，是怎樣的，有巴絲知道嗎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d2665c50e48aacb7ba0ead63010d0f243a6fa4f","tid":166413,"uid":45285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T06:00:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>按一般既僱傭合約。<br />\n<br />\n如果我辭了職，在通知期內，lets say 表現不達標，公司可否炒我？<br />\n<br />\n如果在未離職時，表現不達標，公司想炒，又要不要賠錢的？<br />\n<br />\n(sorry 我沒有提供僱傭合約，但如果按一般情況，是怎樣的，有巴絲知道嗎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n理論上，不論表現，要炒你一定有通知期/代通知金"},{"pid":"14205e932d1d94a88a98c5883656fd7db012611a","tid":166413,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T06:08:29.000Z","msg":"佢主動話 Term 你，一定要補錢。<br />\n<br />\n通常啲公司都唔會咁ON9，只會同你講大家縮短個通知期，俾你提早走。<br />\n<br />\n當然你有權唔應承。"},{"pid":"fcf1fb9ec983a431f0bb1fc865a4ef52f94fc639","tid":166413,"uid":60635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T06:33:28.000Z","msg":"通常唔會咁on9 ，除非你專登攪破壞姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2357b912ecf13936301999c5310fb62582b9d0fa","tid":166413,"uid":68430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T12:58:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc0546e806f5e05f465e0c75df6aa0bc40d8aebf","tid":166413,"uid":29093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T13:00:01.000Z","msg":"你自己都主動走啦,  點會特登炒你賠錢畀你走 ?"},{"pid":"b67103cfb918131c95bd507be669ad4d930e5bdf","tid":166413,"uid":68430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T13:08:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你自己都主動走啦,  點會特登炒你賠錢畀你走 ?</blockquote><br />\n炒我，但俾我通知期，是不用賠錢嘛?"},{"pid":"4ba779b7d96a5db9fc90825fdf25a1c64399632d","tid":166413,"uid":68430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T16:44:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>通常唔會咁on9 ，除非你專登攪破壞姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b8ba5b67cb2ca311bfbc6a44bf8d9c3f746991f","tid":166413,"uid":2020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T16:47:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>你自己都主動走啦,  點會特登炒你賠錢畀你走 ?</blockquote><br />\n炒我，但俾我通知期，是不用賠錢嘛?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔明<br />\n<br />\n你通知期都要出糧 <br />\n<br />\n賠錢果舊錢就係即時趕你走既錢黎<br />\n<br />\n所謂賠錢係代通知金 豪份糧比你 叫你快d滾"},{"pid":"263c28ffe53ff800fa006db2310c6fddd0957820","tid":166413,"uid":92998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T05:24:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢主動話 Term 你，一定要補錢。<br />\n<br />\n通常啲公司都唔會咁ON9，只會同你講大家縮短個通知期，俾你提早走。<br />\n<br />\n當然你有權唔應承。</blockquote><br />\n可以點樣唔應承? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"729d7524dec06b0b17c48b4acbea8f3d5d7e9758","tid":166413,"uid":48623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T05:29:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>你自己都主動走啦,  點會特登炒你賠錢畀你走 ?</blockquote><br />\n炒我，但俾我通知期，是不用賠錢嘛?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n理論上大家一個月通知期就得，但通常公司怕員工玩野就補錢比你即時走（炒你）。理論上你無得唔接受，等於你辭職公司唔可以唔比你辭職一樣。"},{"pid":"375ed8f1fc6a92bc66b9fea7733dfb82c4411fb6","tid":166413,"uid":68430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T14:56:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>你自己都主動走啦,  點會特登炒你賠錢畀你走 ?</blockquote><br />\n炒我，但俾我通知期，是不用賠錢嘛?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n理論上大家一個月通知期就得，但通常公司怕員工玩野就補錢比你即時走（炒你）。理論上你無得唔接受，等於你辭職公司唔可以唔比你辭職一樣。</blockquote><br />\n不過係公司紀錄仍然係自行離職嗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a87966ecd894c809092b7f9d6d27cea3710923fa","tid":166413,"uid":61748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T03:35:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}